@startuml
title Diagrama de Despliegue: Topología propuesta
node "Cliente - Navegador" as Browser
node "Hosting Frontend (Vercel/CDN)" as FrontendNode
node "API Server (Docker)" as APINode
node "Supabase (DB + Storage + Auth)" as SupabaseNode
node "Proveedor LLM (Gemini API)" as LLMNode

Browser --> FrontendNode: HTTPS
FrontendNode --> APINode: HTTPS (REST)
APINode --> SupabaseNode: SQL / Storage (HTTPS)
APINode --> LLMNode: HTTPS (API)
APINode --> APINode: Workers / Queue (background tasks)
@enduml
